{
  "stem": "15991.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned more in that year than I did up to then in the entire school year, I think.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just marvelous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had various teachers and very dedicated, very knowledgeable people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was marvelous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at home we were not allowed to have any non-Jewish servants and had to be very careful in that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to sit on park benches, I remember, not allowed to talk to anyone who's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It became quite restricted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- yes, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I'm sure he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not discussed, or it was discussed in the privacy of [? that. ?]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was the same with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandpa-- father-- the factory belonged to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he was affected by it just the same way my father was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that all stopped on the 11th of November during the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my experience on the night was nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to sleep and didn't know about anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the next morning when my father got out of the train at the station in [GERMAN], he was taken by SS people and incarcerated in a concentration camp, together was two other partners.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, one was my uncle, maternal uncle, Erwin Shaeffer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one was a Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Levy, and he was the engineer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Oranienburg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It with near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then that of course was a devastating moment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was there three or four months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through my mother-- got word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She talked to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she mainly talked to us in the-- I remember-- in the bathroom and while the water was running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, she was very afraid that people would hear.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
